(23648, 'Project Manager for iGrasp Replacement', 'Hello,\n \nATOS is planning to replace current Recruiting tool IGrasp. \nWe are searching a project manager to be responsible for RFP period \nand implementation of the new tool in 3 waves.\nProcess definition will be finalized in January so we need to start in February. \nWe need a colleague who is/ has\n- familiar with global recruitment processes within ATOS\n- familiar with stake holder of our global recruiting landscape\n- deep knowledge about recruiting tools in general \n- knowledge about other HR systems used by ATOS (e.g. Nessie HR) to define and implement required interfaces\n- good communication skills to be clear to phrase our requirements and identify quick wins\n \n \nBest regards\nJulien', 'FR21811', 'RUTTEN Maureen NL25888', '1970-01-01', '1970-01-01', ' - Languages\nEnglish-Business Fluent\n - Activities\nProject management-Level 3 - Apply, IT management-Level 2 - Assist\n - Methods and Standards\nOrganization Communication-Medior', '   ', '', '', '3', '6'),
