(25038, 'MS_PP_PROGRAM_TRANSITIONS&TRANSFORMATION_ChefdeProjet_1_ALSTHOM_ASIE_JEANPIERREPROVOST', 'The Deployment Project Manager is appointed by the Project Director who defines his limits of responsibility and authority and decides in case of unclear responsibility/authority items.\nThe Deployment Project Manager ''s prime responsibility is to ensure that the rollout of Win7 migration is performed  in  time, within budget, service capacities, agreed volume boundaries and to the right level of quality according to contract.\nThe Deployment Project Manager reports, escalates to and takes direction from the Project Manager.\nDeployment Project Manager ''s responsibility starts with a written assignment and ends with end of mass rollout sign-off for the geographical scope.\nDeployment Project Manager ''s responsibility and authority is limited to his assigned geographical area.\n', 'FR25715', 'FOURMY Nathalie S236043', '1970-01-01', '1970-01-01', ' - Languages\nEnglish', 'PM ', '', '', '5', '6'),
